AboutUsDesc: is an E-Commerce website with headquarters in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. Skien.sa.com is a branch of Skien.com.kw which is a committed organization, privately owned and an extremely popular and respected online retailer within Kuwait. It is also considered to be the largest online retailer of the region. Skien is a special division of the organization known as WB Technologies. This company has been considered to be the leading organization in the internet technology industry for well over a decade. Skien Saudi Arabia specializes in a wide range of products, offered at the most competitive prices. Hailed as the most “complete” internet shopping experience.
AboutUsKuwait: is an international electronic commerce company with headquarters in Kuwait. It’s the largest online retailer in the Middle East. Currently serving Kuwait, Saudi Arabia, U.A.E., Qatar, Oman, Bahrain, Egypt, Lebanon and Jordan. Skien.com.kw started as an online computer and accessories store, but soon diversified, selling electronics, software, video games, stationery & office supplies, women’s apparel and fashion accessories, food and toys.We’re the most complete online shopping experience in the Middle East.
